caption: We hope your first week of classes went well! Our first meeting will be on Monday, September 16th, at 4 p.m. in OI C154. The meeting theme will be Impromptu Speeches. We encourage individuals of all comfort levels with public speaking to join. We hope to see you there!

Hope everyone is having a great start to the semester and had a relaxing summer. After our usual summer hiatus, the UofT Poker Club is back and ready to begin the next academic year kicking off with our Inaugural tournament. 

The event will be held in the Innis Events Room on September 13th starting at 6PM with prizing, future tournament rebuys and dinner provided!

For anyone new to the club, feel free to send me any questions and there will be a post later this week/a short spiel at the tournament to explain how the club runs, our schedule and yearly plan;

Please join our discord through our linktree in our bio to receive constant communication, updates, and sign-up sheets for these and any future events.
